EVPP 543: Tropical Ecosystems. 4 credits.
Terrestrial, aquatic, and marine ecosystems in the tropics, emphasizing plant communities, plant-animal interactions, and role of humans in tropics.Notes: Requires field trip to tropics as part of lab. Offered by Environmental Science & Policy. May not be repeated for credit. Equivalent to BIOL 543.
