Grading: This course is graded on the Graduate Regular scale.

EVPP 637: Human Dimensions of Climate Change. 3 credits.
Examines human dimensions of climate change, biodiversity loss, ozone depletion, and related anthropogenic alterations of biosphere. Offered by Environmental Science & Policy. May not be repeated for credit.
