EVPP 648: Population Ecology. 3 credits.
Surveys ecological models and theory. Topics include population growth and regulation, competition, predator-prey, herbivore-plant, and parasite-host interactions, mutualism, and metapopulation ecology. Offered by Environmental Science & Policy. May not be repeated for credit. Equivalent to BIOL 648.
