EVPP 677: Applied Ecology and Ecosystem Management. 3 credits.
Uses ecological principles to manage natural resources. Emphasizes hierarchical levels of organization within ecological systems, and management of ecosystems to conserve biodiversity, natural resources, and environment. Offered by Environmental Science & Policy. May not be repeated for credit.
